00:58:35,000 --> 00:58:37,000
 Kužiš, da.

1195
00:58:37,000 --> 00:58:39,000
 Kužim, kužim.

1196
00:58:39,000 --> 00:58:41,000
 Mi tu sad možemo ući u priču

1197
00:58:41,000 --> 00:58:43,000
 od deset sati i ne bi ni pol temi.

1198
00:58:43,000 --> 00:58:45,000
 Ne, ne.

1199
00:58:45,000 --> 00:58:47,000
 Ali znaš kaj je meni najsretnija

1200
00:58:47,000 --> 00:58:49,000
 recimo iz mog djetnjstva?

1201
00:58:49,000 --> 00:58:51,000
 Na Bajarić, na ribe.

1202
00:58:51,000 --> 00:58:53,000
 Da.

1203
00:58:53,000 --> 00:58:55,000
 Bilo dijić.

1204
00:58:55,000 --> 00:58:57,000
 To mi je ono najsretnija

1205
00:58:57,000 --> 00:58:59,000
 memorija mog djetnjstva

1206
00:58:59,000 --> 00:59:01,000
 na ribama.

1207
00:59:01,000 --> 00:59:03,000
 Kaj je najgore, ono dođe 5, 6, 7 drugih likova.

1208
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:05,000
 Ne znate se.

1209
00:59:05,000 --> 00:59:07,000
 Bećemo cijeli dan, čovječe.

1210
00:59:07,000 --> 00:59:09,000
 I vatamo ribe i boli razbriga.

1211
00:59:09,000 --> 00:59:11,000
 Tako smo se upoznavali.

1212
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:13,000
 Drugo vrijeme, totalno druga ekipa

1213
00:59:13,000 --> 00:59:15,000
 i, nažalost,

1214
00:59:15,000 --> 00:59:17,000
 mi smo zastarili.

1215
00:59:17,000 --> 00:59:19,000
 Biće toga još.

1216
00:59:19,000 --> 00:59:20,000
 Biće.

1217
00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:21,000
 Ali sad, veli, morate prekinuti.

1218
00:59:21,000 --> 00:59:22,000
 Moramo prekinuti.

1219
00:59:22,000 --> 00:59:23,000
 Ništa ljudi, eto.

1220
00:59:23,000 --> 00:59:25,000
 Bilo ovo u meni, baš mi je bilo.

1221
00:59:25,000 --> 00:59:26,000
 Nisam u tim vodama.

1222
00:59:26,000 --> 00:59:28,000
 Nešto sam me naučio.

1223
00:59:28,000 --> 00:59:30,000
 Ljudi ništa, zrce tu.

1224
00:59:30,000 --> 00:59:32,000
 Od repa će nam nešto dole na kavi.

1225
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:34,000
 Nema više tehničkih poteškoća.

1226
00:59:34,000 --> 00:59:36,000
 Jepili smo to rešit.

1227
00:59:36,000 --> 00:59:37,000
 Hvala bok.

1228
00:59:37,000 --> 00:59:38,000
 Pozdrav ekipa bok.

